<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 33 (July 29th, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Kel now has a passive:</li><ul><li><b>The Shepherd -</b> Whenever Kel is hit by a basic attack, the cooldowns of all of his abilities are reduced by 0.25 seconds. The cooldown reduction effect is reduced to 0.1 seconds for attacks from non-shapers.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 32 (July 9th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Titanic Charge (R)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the final damage dealt by this ability to the primary target was incorrectly flagged as AoE damage.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 29 (May 5th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Sheep Toss (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Fixed a visual beg where Kel's Sheep would not appear properly if an enemy Kel used this ability from out of vision.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Sheep Toss (Q)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 850, from previous value of 950.</li></ul><li>Battle Cry! (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 580, from previous value of 650.</li></ul><li>Crook Sweep (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 340, from previous value of 380.</li></ul><li>Titanic Charge (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 450, from previous value of 550.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.7, down from 0.9</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 16 (Oct 31, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Tightened the visual effects on Crook Sweep (E) to more accurately depict the radius of the ability.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 11 (August 29, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Battle Cry! (W)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 60/95/130/165/200, down from 70/105/140/175/210.</li><li>The slow percentage applied by this ability has been reduced to 50/55/60/65/70%, down from 61/67/73/79/85%.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 10 (August 23, 2013)</h4><ul><li>The Haste ratio on all of Kel's abilities have been reduced to 0.5, down from 0.6.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 7 (August 02, 2013)</h4><ul><li>Basic attack range increased to 130, up from 95.</li></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 3 (June 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Titanic Charge (R)</B></li><ul><li>Single target base damage increased to 175/275/375, up from 150/225/300. Pass through damage increased to 150/225/300, up from 110/180/250.</li></ul></ul>